T02TD3630E:247b-1: krishna ya m'a ri s'a dha nam /
T02TD3630E:247b-3: gshin rje dgra nag po'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3630E:247b-4: bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3630E:247b-5: dpa' bo thod pa'i phreng ba can //
T02TD3630E:247b-6: sbrul sogs rgyan gyis rngam byas pa'i //
T02TD3630E:247b-7: gshin rje gshed mgon phyag 'tshal nas //
T02TD3630E:247b-8: de yi sgrub thabs bri bar bya //
T02TD3630E:247b-9: bde ba'i stan la yang dag 'dug / snying gar nyi ma h'um yig dgod //
T02TD3630E:247b-10: der skyes mchod pa'i khyad par gyis //
T02TD3630E:247b-11: gus pas khyab bdag yang dag mchod//
T02TD3630E:247b-12: de yi mdun du phyogs byas te //
T02TD3630E:247b-13: sdig pa bshags pa la sogs bya //
T02TD3630E:247b-14: 'gro kun rang bzhin med par ni //
T02TD3630E:247b-15: skad cig gis bltas de nyid las //
T02TD3630E:247b-16: snying ga'i sa bon rtags las byung //
T02TD3630E:247b-17: zhabs kyi chu skyes g-yon brkyang ba //
T02TD3630E:247b-18: khro gnyer bsdus shing zhal 'jigs la //
T02TD3630E:247b-19: sma ra smin ma dbu skra ser //
T02TD3630E:247b-20: zhal gsum ljags ni bskyod pa yis //
T02TD3630E:247b-21: 'jigs byed mche ba gtsigs pa can //
T02TD3630E:247b-22: spyan ni dmar zhing gsus chen la //
T02TD3630E:247b-23: sprin nag gsar ba'i 'od zer can //
T02TD3630E:247b-24: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la gnas shing //
T02TD3630E:247b-25: ma he yi ni mtshan la bzhugs //
T02TD3630E:247b-26: stag gi sham thabs mi'u thung //
T02TD3630E:248a-2: nyi ma'i 'od zer gzi mdangs che //
T02TD3630E:248a-3: sa steng ma lus kun du mchod //
T02TD3630E:248a-5: dus mtha' yi ni me dang mtshungs //
T02TD3630E:248a-6: rdo rje ral gri gtun shing drag / ro langs sta re zhags pa bsnams //
T02TD3630E:248a-7: phyag g-yas dang ni g-yon pa yi //
T02TD3630E:248a-8: drug po rnams su mdzes par bsnams //
T02TD3630E:248a-9: khro bcas 'jigs byed shin tu drag / gshin rje mthar byed bdud 'joms pa //
T02TD3630E:248a-10: h'um yig gis gang mgrin bsams nas //
T02TD3630E:248a-11: 'dir ni de yi nga rgyal bya //
T02TD3630E:248a-12: snying gar nyi rdor snying 'od kyis //
T02TD3630E:248a-13: gshin rje sdang ba bza' bar bya //
T02TD3630E:248a-14: mdun phyogs de nas mchod nas ni //
T02TD3630E:248a-15: rang dang rnam pa gcig byas te //
T02TD3630E:248a-17: yang dag dgug dang gzhug pa dang //
T02TD3630E:248a-18: bcing dang mnyes pas bdag mchod cing //
T02TD3630E:248a-19: bsam gtan gyis ni mchod byas nas //
T02TD3630E:248a-20: yang dag bstod nas sngags bzlas bya //
T02TD3630E:248a-21: dge ba yongs su bsngo bya zhing //
T02TD3630E:248a-22: langs nas lha yi rnal 'byor gyis //
T02TD3630E:248a-23: brtse ba gcig pu'i yid kyis spyad //
T02TD3630E:248a-24: de bzhin nyi ma so sor bya //
T02TD3630E:248a-25: dngos grub thob pa'i mtshan ma 'byung //
T02TD3630E:248a-26: 'dod pa'i dngos grub bsgrub bya ba //
T02TD3630E:248a-27: las mchog rab tu brkyang na yang //
T02TD3630E:248a-28: las kyi rjes su 'brangs ba'i tshul //
T02TD3630E:248a-29: mangs pas kho bos ma bshad do //
T02TD3630E:248a-30: bla ma'i man ngag de yang ni //
T02TD3630E:248a-31: rgyud las mngon 'dod bsgrub par bya //
T02TD3630E:248a-32: mkhas pas 'khor lo gzhan rnams kyang //
T02TD3630E:248a-33: kun nas 'bad pas shes par bya //
T02TD3630E:248a-34: gtor ma nyer spyod rnal 'byor gyis //
T02TD3630E:248a-35: thun mtshams bzhi ru cho ga bya //
T02TD3630E:248a-37: aom hr'i:shtr'i:bi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD3630E:248a-38: bdag gi bla ma'i man ngag las rtogs nas //
T02TD3630E:248a-39: sgrub thabs cho ga byas pa'i bsod nams kyis //
T02TD3630E:248a-40: 'jig rten pa rnams thams cad gyur pa 'dis //
T02TD3630E:248a-41: mngon par 'dod pa'i 'bras bu myur thob shog / gshin rje'i dgra nag po'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
